            <fr:title text="Naturality of homotopies">Naturality of <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0014.xml" title="Homotopy" addr="forest://erct/erct-0014" type="local">homotopies</fr:link></fr:title>
